snippet.title: Minecraft Adventure Time Mash-Up pack!
snippet.description: It's Adventure Time! Join Finn the human and Jake the dog in a Minecraft world like no other. Protect the candy citizens of Ooo from some familiar foes, or run amok in the colourful wonders of the Adventure Time universe! Coming soon to Pocket, Win 10 and console!
